---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout';
import ProgressBar from '../../components/ProgressBar';
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Cycle 0: 개요 - 개발 여정의 시작"
  description="프로그래밍을 처음 시작하는 분들을 위한 학습 로드맵"
  currentPath="/cycle/0-overview"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8">
    <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-secondary mb-6">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">홈</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <a href="/cycle" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">학습 사이클</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span class="text-primary font-medium">Cycle 0: 개요</span>
    </nav>

    <header class="mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-border">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold mb-4">
        🎯 Cycle 0
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-4">
        개발 여정의 시작
      </h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">
        프로그래밍을 전혀 몰라도 괜찮습니다.
        Choorai의 학습 사이클을 따라가면 누구나 웹 서비스를 만들 수 있습니다.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <Callout client:load variant="tip" title="두 가지 학습 경로">
        <div class="mt-2 space-y-3">
          <p>
            <strong class="text-white">📚 학습 로드맵</strong>: 프로그래밍 기초부터 차근차근 배우고 싶다면
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-white">🚀 서비스 사이클</strong>: 바로 서비스를 만들고 배포하고 싶다면 (60분 완주 후 추천)
          </p>
        </div>
      </Callout>
    </section>

    <article class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <!-- 📚 학습 로드맵 -->
      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          📚 학습 로드맵 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-text-secondary">(기초부터 차근차근)</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Level 0 -->
          <div class="p-6 bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 rounded-xl">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-background font-bold text-lg shrink-0">
                0
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Level 0: 도구 준비</h3>
                <p class="text-text-secondary mb-3">
                  개발에 필요한 도구들을 설치하고 기본 사용법을 익힙니다.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-surface rounded text-xs text-text-secondary">Antigravity / VS Code</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-surface rounded text-xs text-text-secondary">Node.js</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-surface rounded text-xs text-text-secondary">Git</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-surface rounded text-xs text-text-secondary">터미널</span>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <a href="/cycle/0-tools" class="text-primary hover:underline text-sm font-medium">
                    도구 설치하기 →
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Level 1~3: 준비 중 -->
          <div class="p-6 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl opacity-70">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-border text-text-secondary font-bold text-lg shrink-0">
                1-3
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Level 1~3: HTML/CSS → JavaScript → React</h3>
                <p class="text-text-secondary mb-3">
                  웹 개발의 기초를 단계별로 학습합니다. 콘텐츠 준비 중입니다.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-text-muted">🔒 준비 중</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 🚀 서비스 사이클 -->
      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          🚀 서비스 사이클 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-text-secondary">(60분 완주 후 심화)</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-text-secondary mb-6">
          <a href="/start/60min" class="text-primary hover:underline">60분 완주</a>로 첫 서비스를 배포한 후,
          실제 운영에 필요한 요소들을 하나씩 추가하세요.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 font-bold">1</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <a href="/cycle/1-dns" class="text-white font-medium hover:text-primary">DNS 설정</a>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">커스텀 도메인 연결</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 font-bold">2</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <a href="/cycle/2-frontend" class="text-white font-medium hover:text-primary">Frontend 배포</a>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Cloudflare Pages 심화</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 font-bold">3</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <a href="/cycle/3-backend" class="text-white font-medium hover:text-primary">Backend 배포</a>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Cloud Run 심화</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/20 text-yellow-400 font-bold">4</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <a href="/cycle/4-database" class="text-white font-medium hover:text-primary">데이터베이스</a>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">영구 저장소 연결</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 font-bold">5</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <a href="/cycle/5-runtime" class="text-white font-medium hover:text-primary">Runtime</a>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">환경 설정 및 시크릿</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/20 text-cyan-400 font-bold">6</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <a href="/cycle/6-ops" class="text-white font-medium hover:text-primary">Ops</a>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">모니터링 및 운영</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 철학 블록 -->
      <section class="mb-10">
        <div class="p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-purple/10 to-primary/10 border border-accent-purple/30 rounded-xl">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            💡 왜 One Cycle인가?
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-text-secondary">
            <p>
              비개발자가 AI로 프로젝트를 시작하면 <strong class="text-white">90%가 "로컬에서 돌아요"에서 멈춘다</strong>.
            </p>
            <p>
              배포, 환경변수, CORS, 운영... 이 모든 걸 한 번에 겪으면 포기하게 된다.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong class="text-primary">이 사이클을 한 번 완주하면</strong>, 두 번째 프로젝트부터는 30분이면 배포까지 간다.
              구조를 알면 AI에게 질문하는 것도 쉬워진다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">왜 이렇게 나눠놨나요?</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">🎯 목표 지향적</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              각 단계마다 명확한 결과물이 있습니다.
              추상적인 이론이 아닌 실제 동작하는 것을 만듭니다.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">📈 점진적 확장</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              60분 완주로 MVP를 만들고, 서비스 사이클로 하나씩 기능을 추가하세요.
              갑자기 어려워지지 않습니다.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">🤖 AI 친화적</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              각 단계에서 AI에게 물어볼 수 있는 프롬프트를 제공합니다.
              모르면 AI에게 물어보세요.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">⏱️ 시간 효율적</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              필요한 것만 배웁니다.
              나중에 필요할 때 더 깊이 파면 됩니다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>

    <nav class="flex items-center justify-between pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="group flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-border hover:bg-surface transition-colors no-underline"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-secondary group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        <div class="text-left">
          <span class="text-xs text-text-secondary">이전</span>
          <span class="block text-sm text-white font-medium">홈으로</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/cycle/0-tools"
        class="group flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-background transition-colors no-underline"
      >
        <div class="text-right">
          <span class="text-xs opacity-70">다음</span>
          <span class="block text-sm font-bold">도구 설치하기</span>
        </div>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
